{"tid":1404531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳戰略地點 - 迴旋處","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:40:22.000Z","uid":93137,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b18f72fc92420141b7c9d600f2a61e70103405f6","tid":1404531,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"大家都好清楚，狗仔調動人手一定會用大量狗車。而將軍澳有兩個迴旋處可以好容易製造塞車，從而拖延班狗進度。如果好好利用將軍澳地理優勢，足以癱瘓整個將軍澳交通。<br />\n<br />\n1. 坑口迴旋處 接駁坑口、寶林、清水灣、工業區等一帶交通，平時少少塞都玩殘半個將軍澳。呢個據點易守難攻，只需要10分鐘阻塞就可以得到擠塞效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 唐明苑 尚徳村迴旋處 路面接駁多個大型商場，不過呢個迴旋處較大，需要更多時間去製造塞車效果。重點係呢度可以逃向維景灣畔，又可以同寶林手足互相支援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有車又想兜下風嘅連登仔女可以考慮一下！"},{"pid":"c9f0143a7d596fa1bed35262cae63498bae6cd48","tid":1404531,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0493f4e57ba7f9fd5cb8f2d804f2c0e2121f38ff","tid":1404531,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b70981807d664dde5bb09f7114c2316a6c67bb87","tid":1404531,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"Tko班藍c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82efe48c3baccb798e86d2794db7af13a2ca787","tid":1404531,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"搭車經過銀綫灣見有road block"},{"pid":"0419330e3530b75beb5e127282ae04ba4e3db01c","tid":1404531,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b70981807d664dde5bb09f7114c2316a6c67bb87","tid":1404531,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"Tko班藍c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"黃大仙都好多黃C，將軍澳一樣大把。"},{"pid":"4d3d85db31d40020563c5105763116fb9bebf9d6","tid":1404531,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82efe4